;Structure determination of this symmetric homodimer was performed iteratively using CYANA3.0. The 20 structures out of 100 with lowest target function were further refined by restrained molecular dynamics/energy minimization in explicit water using CNS 1.1. Residual dipolar couplings were applied at all stages of the structure determination.
;
